\s Yesu Wankunze, sinz’ icakunkundishije!
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu \bd*\bd Wankunze\bd*\bd , \bd*\bd sinz’ \bd*\bd icakunkundishije! Mukiza mwiza, Yesu wankunze ntabibereye, Waje gukiza abanyavyaha, Kuko wancunguye nokwigura. \bd*
\pc \bdit Ngushime Yesu, nze mpore ngushimagiza Mukiza mwiza, Ngushime Yesu ngushimagize, Ngushime Yesu, Mukiza mwiza, Nzokuririmbir\bdit*\bdit ’\bdit*\bdit  ibihe vyose.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Warankijije ntari mbibereye namba; Mukiza mwiza, Warankijije ntabibereye, War\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  impongano y\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd ivyaha vyanje Hamwe wampfira ku musaraba. \bd*
