\zoli1 \bd Ni w\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd undongora ko ntaz\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  inzira y\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd iyo nja: Mukiza mwiza. Ni w\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd undongora ko ntaz\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  inzira: Ngukurikire ah\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd uja hose, Ari mu nzira nziza canke mbi. \bd*
