\zoli1 \bd Uzomp\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  impera nsohoy\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  i wawe mw ijuru. Mukiza mwiza, Uzomp\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  impera nshitse mw ijuru, Maze nzobona ivyiza vyawe, Nguhimbazanye n\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd abera bose. \bd*
\pc \bdit Ngushime Yesu, nze mpore ngushimagiza Mukiza mwiza, Ngushime Yesu ngushimagize, Ngushime Yesu, Mukiza mwiza, Nzokuririmbir’ ibihe vyose.\bdit*
